      <div class="imgside"><img class="img2" alt="image of product taken apart" src="img/meterhome2.png"></div>
    </div>
    <p>++ We made sure to have the utility names clearly labeled along with the colour and icons so as to cater to the colour-blind.</p>
    <p><br></p>
