    <div class="block">
    <h3>Reflection</h3>
    <p>Balancing working on this project with my day job was an interesting experience. The more I worked on the project, the more I wanted to deep dive into the topic of energy conservation. I couldn't help but discuss it over lunch with my colleagues at times. <br><br>This project taught me a lot about taking ownership of a project and designing a native iOS app concept from scratch. I eagerly await seeing some of our efforts reflected in the developed app one day. </p>
